      public static void registerExchangeKindTypes(IExchangeKindType[] types)
      Registers the application-specific exchange kind types for JSON deserialization. This must be called during application startup before any GTNetEntity instances are deserialized from JSON.
      Parameters:
      types - the array of exchange kind type enum values from the application

    • setEntityKind

      public void setEntityKind(Object value)
      Sets the entity kind from JSON deserialization. Accepts either a numeric byte value or a string enum name. When a string is provided, it is resolved using the registered exchange kind types.
      Parameters:
      value - the entity kind as a Number (byte value) or String (enum name)
      Throws:
      IllegalArgumentException - if the string value cannot be resolved to an exchange kind
